  "remarks": "Former Vice President of Syria from 2006 to 2014.\nFormer member of Syrian Ba’ath Party High Command from 2000 to 2013.; Listing: Designated under the Autonomous Sanctions Regulations 2011 on 2 March 2012. Formerly listed on the RBA Consolidated List as 2011SYR0007. Instrument of first\ndesignation and\ndeclaration:\nAutonomous Sanctions (Designated Persons and Entities and\nDeclared Persons – Syria) List 2012 [F2012L00482]\nRelisted on 12 January 2024.",
